# MoveMate Fitness App – Business Requirements Document (BRD)

This BRD outlines the proposed business and technical requirements for MoveMate, a mobile fitness app designed to help users track workouts, set fitness goals, 
and stay motivated through gamification and social features.


## 🔍 What's Included
- Project overview and business drivers
- In-scope and out-of-scope items
- Stakeholder identification
- Functional & non-functional requirements
- Financial forecast tailored for investors


## ✨ Skills Applied
- BRD Structure & Writing
- Business and Financial Impact Analysis

📂 This project is part of my Business Analysis learning journey and hands-on portfolio.

